{
  "name": "[Test] Smartling Trigger - Asset Exported",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Asset Exported Trigger\n\n**Category:** Integrations Platform\n**Event:** `integrations.platform.asset.exported`\n\n### Payload Fields\n- `account.accountUid` / `account.accountName`\n- `project.projectUid` / `project.projectName` / `project.projectTypeCode`\n- `project.sourceLocale` / `project.targetLocales[]`\n- `asset.integrationId` — connector type (e.g. shopify)\n- `asset.fileUri` — file URI in Smartling\n- `asset.assetUid` — internal asset identifier\n- `asset.externalAssetId` — external CMS identifier (nullable)\n- `asset.targetLocales[]` — locales exported\n\n### Setup\n1. Assign your **Smartling API** credential\n2. Optionally select project(s) to filter\n3. **Activate** the workflow to register the webhook\n4. Export an asset from a connector project to trigger\n\nNote: Webhook triggers require activation. Use ngrok for local testing."
      },
      "id": "note-1",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-20, -220]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "event": "integrations.platform.asset.exported",
        "projectUids": []
      },
      "id": "trigger-1",
      "name": "Smartling Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-smartling.smartlingTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [0, 0],
      "webhookId": "",
      "credentials": {
        "smartlingApi": {
          "id": "",
          "name": "Smartling API"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "duplicateItem": false,
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "out-event",
              "name": "eventType",
              "value": "={{ $json.eventType }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-projectUid",
              "name": "projectUid",
              "value": "={{ $json.project?.projectUid }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-projectType",
              "name": "projectTypeCode",
              "value": "={{ $json.project?.projectTypeCode }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-integrationId",
              "name": "integrationId",
              "value": "={{ $json.asset?.integrationId }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-fileUri",
              "name": "fileUri",
              "value": "={{ $json.asset?.fileUri }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-assetUid",
              "name": "assetUid",
              "value": "={{ $json.asset?.assetUid }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-externalAssetId",
              "name": "externalAssetId",
              "value": "={{ $json.asset?.externalAssetId }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-targetLocales",
              "name": "exportedLocales",
              "value": "={{ $json.asset?.targetLocales?.map(l => l.localeId).join(', ') }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "out-timestamp",
              "name": "receivedAt",
              "value": "={{ new Date().toISOString() }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "output-1",
      "name": "Log Event",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [220, 0]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Smartling Trigger": {
      "main": [[{ "node": "Log Event", "type": "main", "index": 0 }]]
    }
  },
  "pinData": {},
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "staticData": null,
  "tags": [],
